    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "（ふふ、今度は瑠依からきたわ。仕事の合間に）\n（わざわざ送ってくれるなんて、律儀ね）",
      "startTime": 7.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7499.999999999999,
          "startTime": 10.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "え、なんか鳴ってると思ったら、莉央のスマホ？\n気をつけた方がいいわよ、変なサイトに登録するの",
      "startTime": 15.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "迷惑メールじゃないわよ。今日、私の誕生日だから\n後輩がお祝いのメッセをくれてるの",
      "startTime": 24.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "（もう、普段はあんまり話しかけてこないのに）\n（急にめちゃくちゃなことを言うわね……）",
      "startTime": 30.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日？　へー、おめでとう。……ねぇ、今時間ある？\nせっかくだし、お祝いにどっかで奢ってあげるわよ",
      "startTime": 41.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5799.999999999997,
          "startTime": 46.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.6166666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.6166666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ん～！　このタルト美味しい！　果物は美容にもいいし\n罪悪感が少ないのがいいわよね。莉央も頼んだら？",
      "startTime": 53.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、その……franさんってお金に汚いって\n聞いていたから、さすがに動揺していて……",
      "startTime": 63.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "汚くないわよ！　がめついとは言われるけど。それも\n言いがかりだわ。ただ、莉央って普段苦労してそうだし",
      "startTime": 71.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "私もセンターでしょ。メンバーには苦労させられてる\nから、莉央の気持ちは分かるのよ。だからそういうこと",
      "startTime": 81.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.7333328247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "一応聞くけど……ここのお代、何かしら理由つけて\nあわよくば経費で落とそうなんて思ってないわよね",
      "startTime": 92.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.466666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "っ……そ、そんな訳ない、とは言い切れないけど\n細かいことはいいじゃない。私が一度払いはするし",
      "startTime": 102.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.966666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "（はぁ……franさんって旅行の時といい本当に自由ね）\n（でも、ある意味素直だし、意外と話しやすいかも？）",
      "startTime": 113.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6399.999999999992,
          "startTime": 119.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.616666158
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.866666158
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.2333318075
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "で？　なんで結局、私が払うことになってる訳？\n私、今日誕生日なんだけど。お祝いのはずよね？",
      "startTime": 126.6666656495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.6666656495
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.6333318075
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "い、今から返すってば。お財布忘れたのは本当だから\nわざわざマンションまでついてこないでよ、返すから",
      "startTime": 135.5333323162,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5633.3333333000155,
          "startTime": 141.1666656495
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.7499984742
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.7499984742
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.7666656495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "へ～、ここがfranさんの……ちょっと、空き巣に\n入られてるじゃない！　何よ、この荒れ方っ！？",
      "startTime": 147.3333323162,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13099.999999999995,
          "startTime": 160.4333323162
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.6999852499
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "入られてないわよ、失礼ね。好奇心丸出しで、無理やり\n上がってきたくせに。とりあえず、はい、お金……くっ",
      "startTime": 156.1666656495,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9000,
          "startTime": 165.1666656495
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.6333323162
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.4966656495
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.0666519166
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.2666656495
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.0999989828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "最初から汚いだけなのね……って、ちょっと渡すつもり\nなら手を離しなさいよ。ん……そのジャケットは？",
      "startTime": 169.7999989828,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3200.013732900004,
          "startTime": 167.2666656495
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.348083400017,
          "startTime": 168.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.9666519166
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、この段ボールの中の？　私がデザインしたやつよ\n黒は黒でも、選び抜いた黒なの。ふふん、いいでしょ",
      "startTime": 181.0666656495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.6666570028
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん。……ねえ、お金はいいから、これもらえない？\nサングラスとかに合わせたら、いい感じになりそう",
      "startTime": 192.0000040691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.7999903362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもう着る気になってるのよ。これ高いのよ！？\n確かに余ってる在庫ではあるけど、そんなほいほい……",
      "startTime": 200.0000040691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.9666559857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、今度どこかの撮影で着てあげるから\nSNS用に、ツーショット撮ってあげてもいいわよ",
      "startTime": 207.8333363852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
